product_description: Introducing a new kid-size body for your Nendoroid dolls! The Nendoroid Doll series of palm-sized action figures feature the same heads as standard Nendoroids, but alternate doll-like bodies that are highly articulated and can easily be dressed up into different outfits! The feet of the Nendoroid Doll body feature magnets in the soles of the feet which allow for easy posing on the included magnetic base, but an articulated stand is also included allowing for more active poses! A longer neck joint is included which can be used for a better appearance when using certain fabric outfits. You can easily attach the head parts of previously released Nendoroids to give your favorite characters a whole new set of display possibilities!
specification: Painted plastic non-scale articulated figure with stand included. Magnets used in some areas. Body is approximately 65mm in height

product_description:
Presenting a second entry in the original transforming figure series "Cyclion", created based on an original concept by Basil no Zoukei Tamashii and designed by Tsuyoshi Nonaka.

The figures are also articulated, making for easy transformation and easy posing.

The plastic model is based on an original design by Akiman carefully brought into model form by Max Factory. Three pre-painted face plates—a standard face, a shouting face and an angry face—are included. An unpainted face plate and eye decals are included as well. Her uniquely designed apron is created with pre-painted PVC parts. Her skirt is also articulated, allowing for unobstructed movement of her legs for posing. Her great spear and shield feature a distinct dragon design. The model comes with arm armor, a waist mounting unit, two swords (for use with Himari) and a short sword. The model can also be displayed without any equipment on. Hand parts are made with flexible PVC. An articulated stand is included to display the model in a variety of poses.
